-- TABLE-Danish Sept retail sales index up 0.5 pct yr/yr
-- By Copenhagen newsroom
-- Wed Oct 22, 2014 03:07AM EDT
-- None



COPENHAGEN, Oct 22 (Reuters) - The Danish retail sales index rose 0.5 percent in September from a year earlier, the statistics office said on Wednesday.

Retail sales fell 0.9 percent in September from the previous month, Statistics Denmark said.Sep 2014 Aug 2014 Pct. change yr/yr +0.5 +1.1 Pct. change mth/mth   -0.9 +0.5**  ** Revised from an initial figure of 0.6 percent.